(1599,1,"2017-03-10 13:05:22","2017-03-10 13:05:22","[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\"][vc_column][vc_banner_title style=\"big\" color_style=\"light\" subtitle=\"VOROHTA, UKRAINE\" title=\"Awesome Design for the Vorokhta Hub\" img=\"15\" button=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Fwp.themedemo.co/prague%2Fwork-grid%2F|title:EXPLORE%20IT|target:%20_blank|\" style_button=\"creative\" enable_overlay=\"true\" enable_fullheight=\"true\" columns=\"%5B%7B%7D%5D\"]The main objective of the project - transformation of Vorokhta City in innovative\n\nSMART CITY (village) and tourist center.[/vc_banner_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row desctop_mt=\"margin-lg-140t\" tablets_mt=\"margin-sm-70t\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\" desctop_mt=\"margin-lg-65t\" tablets_mt=\"margin-sm-0t\" offset=\"vc_col-lg-offset-0 vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-offset-0 vc_col-md-5 vc_col-sm-offset-2 vc_col-xs-12\"][vc_counters image_background=\"191\" border_size=\"15px\" numbers=\"%5B%7B%22number%22%3A%2214%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22YEARS%20OF%20EXPERIENCE%22%7D%5D\"][/vc_column][vc_column tablets_mt=\"margin-sm-20t\" offset=\"vc_col-lg-offset-1 vc_col-lg-7 vc_col-md-offset-0 vc_col-md-7 vc_col-sm-offset-0 vc_col-xs-12\"][vc_headings subtitle=\"ABOUT US\" title=\"Break out of your routine with\na global perspective.\" enable_animated=\"true\"]Based on collective work and shared knowledge, Architecture-Studio aims to favour dialogue and debate, to transform individual knowledge into increased creative potential.\n\nOur Studio is a architecture practice based in Prague, Chech and Venice. Today, it includes 150 architects, urban planners, landscape and interior designers of 25 different nationalities. The company principle of Architecture-Studio is the collective conception. From the very beginning, the practice has believed in the virtues of exchange, crossing ideas, common effort, shred knowledge.[/vc_headings][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row desctop_mt=\"margin-lg-15t\" tablets_mt=\"margin-sm-20t\"][vc_column][vc_headin